result.description:
One document with all information from the sub WPs mentioned in the work package.
The report will collect the state of the art in Italy and Europe of:
- the current biogas and biomethane scenario in Italy and assessment of the residual biomass potential;
- technical background on biogas and biomethane production and gas grid injection, and best practices;
- use of digestate and best practices;
- participatory process in energy field and best practices.
